{"tid":2231135,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩男女生堵路罪不成立 官：兩警證供矛盾、不可靠不可信","createTime":"2020-10-05T12:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T12:44:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23eed6589569190336ab6aabe88d208d2fa17004","tid":2231135,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077916&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZLygGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=2b597800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077916&h=14b0300d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077916</a><br />\n<br />\n裁判官張天雁指，拘捕16歲女生的警員黎錦耀的證供不可信不可靠，女生當日究竟與另外3個人還是與4至5個人一同堵路，黎在庭上多次作出更改。此外，黎就第一眼目睹女生時的行為的口供也多次作出更改，口供紙未有提及她有否戴口罩，惟黎警員在庭上卻堅稱女生有戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n另外，黎警員供稱女生當場承認「要爭取五大訴求」、「我知非法堵路係唔啱嘅，俾次機會我啦」；辯方則稱女生被警員制服在地上時，遭用力膝跪背脊，呼吸困難，因此不可能說出相關說話。張官早前基於黎的證供不可靠，已剔除女生的招認口供。"},{"pid":"2c5493b65ac0ca56c78413dad26848f812df88fd","tid":2231135,"uid":6132,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T12:29:52.000Z","msg":"矛盾代表冇夾口供喎<br />\n個法官識唔識㗎"},{"pid":"3763c22322c0577f70aaf105ff1a2eddba0e8d29","tid":2231135,"uid":76804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"次次都不可靠不可信<br />\n次次都有曬證據濫暴用私刑<br />\n然後無事繼續鳩告"},{"pid":"9315b010683dcb6fb84eaf53608b04790dbcda77","tid":2231135,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"兩狗證供矛盾 另一邊窗反而係誠實可靠 另一邊就不盡不實"},{"pid":"e8f7851651156dbc8f451d1e164b3e2d6b332ec1","tid":2231135,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾連傷心柴都畀人搣埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ww